I have noticed that time to time my kubernetas pod faced Out of memory exception. Regarding to Grafana it starts with 500 Mb and reach 6 Gb after some times of processing of queue of learning.

Then I have tried to reproduce the problem on my local machine and looks like I have found a problem by memory profiling:

    // Call AutoML learning inside
